# ==============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS — required review for the shared CI surface
# ==============================================================================
# A change to anything under .github/ ripples out to every repo that consumes
# these reusable workflows, so those paths require explicit owner review.
# Enforced only when the matching branch protection rule has
# "Require review from Code Owners" enabled.
#
# Owned by the @NeuralTrust/platform team. Members of that team are managed in
# GitHub org settings, so this file does not need editing when people join/leave.
# ==============================================================================

# Reusable workflows and composite actions — the security-critical surface.
/.github/workflows/   @NeuralTrust/platform
/.github/actions/     @NeuralTrust/platform
/.github/dependabot.yml   @NeuralTrust/platform
/.github/CODEOWNERS       @NeuralTrust/platform
